"電子は原子を構成する粒子。質量: m[sub]e[/sub]=(9.1093897± 0.0000054)e-31 kg "
"負電荷: [i]e[/i]=(1.60217733 ±0.00000049)e-19 C\n"
"\t\t"

#. +> trunk6 stable6
#: data/knowledge.xml:220
#, fuzzy, kde-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The proton is a subatomic particle with a mass of m[sub]e[/"
